long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Game Controls
Master the controls to navigate the pirate’s life:

Arrow Keys or WASD: Control the movement of your pirate.
Mouse: Aim and shoot during naval battles.
Interact with Objects: Use the E key to interact with objects, open chests, and more.
How to Play
Create Your Pirate: Customize your pirate character, choosing your appearance and outfit.
Embark on Voyages: Accept quests and set sail on voyages to discover buried treasure and face challenges.
Naval Battles: Engage in thrilling ship-to-ship battles, using cannons to defeat rival pirates.
Build Your Pirate Legend: Complete quests, amass wealth, and increase your pirate reputation to become a legendary captain.
